  <description><![CDATA[<p>境外的购物网站很多都不支持中国银联的银行卡，而中国银行长城跨境通借记卡是一个可以在线申请、没有申请门槛也没有年费的卡。</p>
<div class="details admonition info open">
    <div class="details-summary admonition-title">
      <i class="icon fa-solid fa-info-circle fa-fw" aria-hidden="true"></i>信息<i class="details-icon fa-solid fa-angle-right fa-fw" aria-hidden="true"></i>
    </div>
    <div class="details-content">
      <div class="admonition-content">我主要在<a href="https://poplite.xyz/post/2018/03/05/boc-debit-card-guide-for-online-payment.html#3-%E7%94%B3%E5%8D%A1%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97"target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">跨境通VISA/万事达借记卡介绍与网上支付体验<i class="fa-solid fa-external-link-alt fa-fw fa-xs ms-1 text-secondary" aria-hidden="true"></i></a>这篇博客上了解到了这个卡，感谢作者的分享。</div>
    </div>
  </div>
